svg.metadata: Created by FontForge 20220308 at Thu May 28 15:37:10 2009 By Unknown Designed at Polygraphmash type design bureau in 1988 by Svetlana Yermolaeva. Based on Kirillitsa (1982), inspired by typographic poluustav of the Printing Office of the Russian Empire Academy of Science (late 19th century). Shadow style was added by Alexander Tarbeev in 1994. Latin alphabet was added by Oleg Karpinsky in 2009.
